    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS system has been comprehensively bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has undergone professional reinforcement to ensure optimal torsional rigidity. It retains the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and an untouched OEM suspension setup with zero compliance issues in the bushings. The interior is immaculate, featuring Nappa leather and a flawless instrument cluster. Full service documentation is included, confirming a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. This is a turn-key, analog performance icon for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
